OL,3,CReeves defends move to cut winter fuel
OL,4,Cpayments as 'right decision'
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves has defended
OL,7,Fthe government's decision to cut
OL,8,Fwinter fuel payments for some
OL,9,Fpensioners, insisting it will be
OL,10,Foffset by increases to pensions and
OL,11,Flower energy prices this winter
OL,12,Fcompared with last year.
OL,14,FReeves said the state pension was
OL,15,Fworth #900 more than in 2023, and that
OL,16,Fit will rise again next April under
OL,17,Fthe triple lock agreement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
