OL,3,CReeves defends move to cut winter fuel
OL,4,Cpayments as 'right decision'
OL,6,FShe said: "We inherited a #22 billion
OL,7,Fblackhole from the previous government
OL,8,Fwho made unfunded spending commitments
OL,9,Fwith no idea how to pay them.
OL,11,F"When I became chancellor I took an
OL,12,Fimmediate audit of the spending
OL,13,Fsituation to understand the scale of
OL,14,Fthat challenge, and I made difficult
OL,15,Fdecisions to put the public finances
OL,16,Fon a sustainable footing.
OL,18,F"They were tough decisions, but they
OL,19,Fwere the right decisions."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
