OL,3,CReeves defends move to cut winter fuel
OL,4,Cpayments as 'right decision'
OL,6,FReeves' comments were criticised by a
OL,7,Fnumber of opposition MPs, with Dame
OL,8,FHarriett Baldwin, Conservative MP for
OL,9,FWest Worcestershire, calling it a
OL,10,F"chilling political choice".
OL,12,FShe said: "Within the first few days
OL,13,Fof coming to office, the chancellor
OL,14,Fmanaged to spend over #22 billion,
OL,15,Fvery quickly, by setting up great
OL,16,FBritish Energy, by setting up a
OL,17,Fnational wealth fund and by giving in
OL,18,Fto the pay demands of her party's
OL,19,Funion paymasters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
