OL,3,CReeves defends move to cut winter fuel
OL,4,Cpayments as 'right decision'
OL,6,F"Is it not the case that this
OL,7,Fchancellor has made the chilling
OL,8,Fpolitical choice to balance the books
OL,9,Fof this country on the very frailest
OL,10,Fshoulders?"
OL,12,FLiberal Democrat Steve Darling,
OL,13,Fmeanwhile, raised concerns about the
OL,14,Fimpact the move will have on
OL,15,Fpensioners, revealing around 21,000
OL,16,Falone in his Torbay constituency will
OL,17,Flose the payment this winter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
