OL,3,CReeves defends move to cut winter fuel
OL,4,Cpayments as 'right decision'
OL,6,F"Whilst many of us would acknowledge
OL,7,Fthat you were left with a massive
OL,8,Ffinancial challenge when coming into
OL,9,Fthis House, one remains extremely
OL,10,Fconcerned for residents who have
OL,11,Freached out to myself and many
OL,12,Fcolleagues with their major concerns
OL,13,Fabout being able to make ends meet as
OL,14,Fwe enter into the winter period," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"They have had no time to save for
OL,18,Fthis, and therefore it's a complete
OL,19,Fshock to them."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
